{"code":200,"message":"OK","tweet":{"url":"https://x.com/canghe/status/2070091940260155651","id":"2070091940260155651","text":"","raw_text":{"text":"https://t.co/ooqD1EBV8K","display_text_range":[0,23],"facets":[]},"author":{"screen_name":"canghe","url":"https://x.com/canghe","id":"1226419222474936320","followers":36526,"following":726,"likes":3481,"media_count":692,"name":"苍何","description":"Founder @wesight_ai\nFormer Alibaba Engineer · Microsoft MVP\nExploring AI global growth & AI-native\nAgents / Skills / MCP / Open Source\nhttps://dinq.me/canghe","raw_description":{"text":"Founder @wesight_ai\nFormer Alibaba Engineer · Microsoft MVP\nExploring AI global growth & AI-native\nAgents / Skills / MCP / Open Source\nhttps://t.co/klsWzMds0c","facets":[{"type":"url","indices":[135,158],"original":"https://t.co/klsWzMds0c","replacement":"https://dinq.me/canghe","display":"dinq.me/canghe"}]},"location":"武汉","banner_url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/1226419222474936320/1707200700","avatar_url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1744283141219680256/5DcrV0du_200x200.jpg","joined":"Sun Feb 09 08:15:56 +0000 2020","protected":false,"website":{"url":"https://canghe.ai","display_url":"canghe.ai"},"verification":{"verified":true,"verified_at":null,"type":"individual"},"avatar_color":null},"replies":5,"retweets":10,"likes":103,"bookmarks":183,"quotes":0,"created_at":"Thu Jun 25 10:29:13 +0000 2026","created_timestamp":1782383353,"possibly_sensitive":false,"views":18740,"is_note_tweet":false,"community_note":null,"lang":null,"replying_to":null,"replying_to_status":null,"source":"Twitter Web App","article":{"created_at":"2026-06-25T10:29:13.000Z","modified_at":"2026-06-25T10:29:32.000Z","id":"2070091201311916032","title":"苍何的 GEO 诊断专家入职腾讯了","preview_text":"花了不少时间做了一个 GEO 诊断的 Skill，不少朋友用完之后反馈说效果不错，但也有人问我：能不能不用折腾安装，开箱即用？\n刚好腾讯 WorkBuddy 团队找到我，说可以把这个 Skill 上架到 WorkBuddy","cover_media":{"id":"QXBpTWVkaWE6DAAFCgABHLpw/ClbcAAKAAIRBR3I9VRQAAAA","media_id":"2070091207058092032","media_info":{"__typename":"ApiImage","color_info":{"palette":[{"percentage":97.66,"rgb":{"blue":253,"green":251,"red":250}},{"percentage":1.04,"rgb":{"blue":219,"green":191,"red":127}},{"percentage":0.41,"rgb":{"blue":208,"green":208,"red":234}},{"percentage":0.3,"rgb":{"blue":184,"green":227,"red":239}},{"percentage":0.16,"rgb":{"blue":124,"green":87,"red":203}}]},"original_img_height":460,"original_img_url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HLpw_ClbcAA3jZy.jpg","original_img_width":1080},"media_key":"3_2070091207058092032"},"content":{"blocks":[{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"vbueq","text":"花了不少时间做了一个 GEO 诊断的 Skill，不少朋友用完之后反馈说效果不错，但也有人问我：能不能不用折腾安装，开箱即用？","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"gv9jn","text":"刚好腾讯 WorkBuddy 团队找到我，说可以把这个 Skill 上架到 WorkBuddy 的专家市场里，直接变成一个人人可用的专家 Agent。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"8vxxv","text":"我马上就安排上线了，现在你打开 WorkBuddy 的专家，就能看到苍何的「品牌 GEO 诊断专家」。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"8brc6","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"dhd4a","text":"你在 WorkBuddy 里面可以召唤这个专家，为你所用，完成你的品牌或者产品的 GEO 一次深度彻底的诊断。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":1,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"zhgla","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"82up8","text":"可能有些朋友还不太了解 GEO，简单说一下。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"nybne","text":"GEO，全称 Generative Engine Optimization，生成式引擎优化。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"n4pph","text":"以前做品牌，你得做 SEO，让用户在百度、Google 搜到你。但现在越来越多的人直接问 AI 了，问元宝、问 DeepSeek，AI 回答里有没有你的品牌，就决定了用户能不能找到你。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":29,"offset":4,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"yvrgl","text":"说白了，GEO 就是让你的品牌能被 AI「记住」并且「推荐」出来。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"r30yw","text":"这也是我为什么要做这个 GEO 诊断的原因，你得先知道自己在 AI 眼里长什么样，才能对症下药。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":2,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"6zikz","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"ejlfl","text":"就拿苍何自己的产品 WeSight 的 GEO 诊断为例吧，当在 WorkBuddy 里面召唤这个 GEO 诊断专家后输入需求：","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"fdvwe","text":"帮我诊断 WeSight 这个产品的 GEO情况，这个是他的官网：，这个是开源项目：","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"wcl9o","text":"他就会加载 GEO 诊断专家技能，开始诊断「WeSight」的 GEO 可见度情况。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":3,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"l9li0","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"zuecn","text":"这个 Skill 会诊断品牌在 AI 搜索/生成式回答里的可见度：品牌是否被提及、提及率如何、数字基建够不够、竞品压力怎样、舆情健康度如何，最后输出 HTML 报告。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"l7hby","text":"所以耗时会相对久一些，我录了个屏，你可以看下出来的诊断效果。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":4,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"0wprw","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"dw6oc","text":"当然也可以在 WorkBuddy 中链接飞书，把诊断报告上传到飞书文档，这是上传到飞书后的效果。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":5,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"o1zph","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"r0vhr","text":"你给 WorkBuddy 的指令可以是：","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"s9f18","text":"帮我传到飞书文档，相关数据展示可以使用飞书图表和白板能力","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":6,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"9k3jf","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"ick8r","text":"除了能诊断产品的 GEO，还可以用来分析诊断 IP 品牌的 GEO 效果，我来「苍何」试了下，目前整体评分是 72 分。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":7,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"yo390","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"yvdgi","text":"我用元宝随便问了下，还是能直接很快搜到了，说明我自己在 GEO 的布局做的还不错。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":8,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"71msz","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"bh1xz","text":"这里也非常建议做 IP 做内容创作的朋友们都来测测目前的分数，可以评论区看下你们的分数是多少。","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"8tekc","text":"当然了，还可以给企业做 GEO 诊断，比如我给火哥公司来一波 GEO 诊断，我录了个屏，你也可以看看这一份报告。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":9,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"4y3rl","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":55,"offset":24,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"d5l3s","text":"整个 GEO 的诊断报告会分几大核心模块，分别是诊断概览、AIVO评分（思维评分模型）、用户画像、搜索可见性、基建评估、竞品分析、收录效果、舆情分析和综合建议。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"tog7a","text":"在诊断概览里，会基于所有要素，给当前品牌或产品一个综合评分和评级，并给到关键发现和风险提示。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":10,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"gdz3s","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"vcqar","text":"特别是一些风险提示，品牌尤其需要关注，比如舆情负面率、竞品情况、品牌认知度问题。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"gyqbb","text":"就比如给 WeSight 做检测的时候，就有一条风险提示是关于 WeSight 仅支持macOS Apple Silicon 的，也会对 AI 搜索会有影响。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":11,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"b05q5","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"6s503","text":"比如给航点这家公司的风险提示就会说的比较一针见血，AI 搜索可见度很低，不知道火哥看完我的文章后会不会加强做 GEO，哈哈。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":12,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"8tine","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"5kvf6","text":"接下来会是从四个维度对品牌进行思维评分模型，分别是 AI 搜索可见度、基建完善度、竞品对比优势、舆情健康度，全面评估品牌整体评分情况。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":13,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"z7pw9","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"h4ci7","text":"比如，这里给 WeSight 检测出的 AIVO 评分是 38分，WeSight 的 GEO表现呈现明显的'冰火两重天'：舆情健康度尚可（78分），但AI搜索可见度（22分）和竞品对比优势（28分）严重拖累总分。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"eqr38","text":"核心矛盾在于产品有差异化价值但无人知晓。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"os7jm","text":"在用户画像模块，这个 Skill 会根据搜索场景去全方面的分析品牌或产品的画像维度。包括年龄分布、牌忠诚度、技术敏感度、付费意愿、技术兴趣。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":14,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"mvpm9","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"68rg3","text":"这个维度是根据搜索场景自动分析做的维度打标，不同产品或品牌的画像维度也不一样。","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"5xdjf","text":"比如在这个 case 里，发现用户在大模型中提问比较多这类话题“有没有能统一管理多个 AI Agent 的桌面软件”。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":6,"offset":32,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"6bjdu","text":"表明实际用户对技术敏感度和技术兴趣度关注更多，这在 GEO 里叫意图漏斗偏移。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"56ce8","text":"用户真实的搜索意图和品牌主打的营销关键词之间存在错位，如果不及时校准内容策略去匹配这些高频真实意图，AI 在生成推荐时就会优先召回更贴合用户语义的竞品。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"1cx3q","text":"在搜索可见性这个地方，会去查询元宝、DeepSeek、豆包、Kimi 等各个平台品牌的提及情况。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":15,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"mcsnn","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"x992x","text":"还会列出问题提及明细。全面评估当前品牌在各个大模型的提及情况，这个地方还是比较花费时间的，特别是我这里选择了全平台，实际费时会更多一些。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"499gw","text":"在 GEO 时代，品牌提及率就是新的「搜索排名」，用户不再翻链接，AI 替他选了，你没被提及，就等于不存在。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"u6jy2","text":"在基建评估这里我认为也非常重要，这里我们暂时设计了三大维度进行评估，分别是官网评估、自媒体矩阵、权威媒体背书。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":16,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"nkh2m","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"vlfz7","text":"在自媒体矩阵这里其实有个小问题，现在为了响应速度并没有做全量，有可能你的品牌有更多的声量，但当前版本先检测基础情况，后续版本还会直接链接具体的文章。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":5,"offset":15,"style":"Bold"},{"length":27,"offset":52,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"9xnz7","text":"这三大维度其实是 GEO 里「可信源覆盖」的核心，大模型在生成回答时会优先引用它认为权威、可信的信息源，官网是第一信源，自媒体是声量放大器，权威媒体是信任背书，三者缺一不可。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"ioxsq","text":"在竞品分析这里，会分析当前品牌或产品的竞品，从可见度到竞品详情，全方位分析竞品的市场份额、威胁等级和产品特点。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":17,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"obyfc","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"p73z2","text":"这里实际跑下来，在可见度评分上还需要优化及响应算法，相信会更准确。","type":"blockquote"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"tvv9p","text":"GEO 竞品分析的核心在于：同一条用户 query 下，AI 把推荐位给了谁，这是一场「语义心智份额」的争夺。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"mmin3","text":"在收录效果这里，会给出几大搜索场景和不同的测试问题，去看各个平台的提及情况，最终算出提及率。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":18,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"2gu20","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"oxysc","text":"收录效果某种意义上是 GEO 的终局指标，前面所有的基建、内容、舆情最终都要落到一个结果上：AI 回答里有没有你。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"fdubb","text":"接下来是舆情分析，这个就更为重要了。因为大模型在生成回答时会做情感倾向加权，负面舆情一旦被模型「学进去」，它在推荐你的品牌时就会自动附带风险提示甚至直接跳过你，而且这种负面印记的消除周期远比传统搜索引擎长得多。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":19,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"vwyis","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"9mssr","text":"需要特别关注舆情问题，然后查看具体的应对策略。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"2cjmq","text":"最后会给出整个的组合建议，从快速赢利点到优先行动建议，会给一些行动建议，比如解决舆情，GEO 曝光补齐等。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":20,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"0v91e","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"huxwo","text":"甚至会给到一些简单版的实施路线图，进行分阶段优化路径。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[{"key":21,"length":1,"offset":0}],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"w636i","text":" ","type":"atomic"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"s2pv6","text":"说实话，现在 GEO 处于早期蛮荒期，不少人用开源项目包一包，套了个壳，就给你假装说自研，然后开始说要给你整 GEO。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"8m3e6","text":"但实际上，很多品牌和企业，是为了 GEO 而 GEO，并没有好好给自己的品牌做一次诊断，就贸然的去做。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"z3ikl","text":"结果就是效果没保证，还没法量化，钱花了，AI 搜索里依然没你的名字。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"3szik","text":"GEO 的正确姿势，一定是先诊断，再治疗。你得先知道自己在 AI 眼里是什么样的，哪些维度有短板，哪些地方被竞品压着，然后才能对症下药。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"jlw8j","text":"这也是我做这个 GEO 诊断专家的初衷：让每个品牌都能用最低的成本，先把自己的 GEO 底子摸清楚。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[{"length":15,"offset":20,"style":"Bold"}],"key":"umwqj","text":"说到底，GEO 时代最大的变化就一句话：用户不再选择，AI 替他选了。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"46may","text":"你能做的，就是让 AI 在替用户选的时候，选的是你。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"qnrfl","text":"如果你也想给自己的品牌或产品做一次 GEO 体检，直接打开 WorkBuddy，召唤「品牌 GEO 诊断专家」就行，欢迎来体验。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"ub0ce","text":"当然了，如果你也有做 GEO 的需求，也欢迎联系苍何，我们沉下心研究 GEO 有一段时间了，只是还比较低调在专心打磨产品，也给不少企业品牌做了 GEO，我们的产品相信很快就能和大家见面了。","type":"unstyled"},{"data":{},"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"y3ak8","text":"觉得有用的话，点个赞，转发给你身边做品牌的朋友，说不定能帮他省一笔冤枉钱。","type":"unstyled"}],"entityMap":[{"key":"12","value":{"data":{"entityKey":"9480a423-7d92-4a57-8558-06c5769b270c","mediaItems":[{"localMediaId":"13","mediaCategory":"DraftTweetImage","mediaId":"2070091105312661504"}]},"mutability":"Immutable","type":"MEDIA"}},{"key":"8","value":{"data":{"entityKey":"3616a4f1-2798-4260-8fc9-61d2e9ee1c77","mediaItems":[{"localMediaId":"9","mediaCategory":"DraftTweetImage","mediaId":"2070091061620518912"}]},"mutability":"Immutable","type":"MEDIA"}},{"key":"19","value":{"data":{"entityKey":"c125fe39-42f4-4479-9b8d-97f338ed9b74","mediaItems":[{"localMediaId":"20","mediaCategory":"DraftTweetImage","mediaId":"2070091174241800192"}]},"mutability":"Immutable","type":"MEDIA"}},{"key":"4","value":{"data":{"entityKey":"5796be7d-24d6-464f-9b83-0401501699fe","mediaItems":[{"localMediaId":"5","mediaCategory":"DraftTweetImage","mediaId":"2070091023955730432"}]},"mutability":"Immutable","type":"MEDIA"}},{"key":"15","value":{"data":{"entityKey":"968bf5b5-0067-4599-b3d0-418e2e540dec","mediaItems":[{"localMediaId":"16","mediaCategory":"DraftTweetImage","mediaId":"2070091135826137088"}]},"mutability":"Immutable","type":"MEDIA"}},{"key":"11","value":{"data":{"entityKey":"8f203cff-2335-4307-a78c-c4c26bb00cd3","mediaItems":[{"localMediaId":"12","mediaCategory":"DraftTweetImage","mediaId":"2070091096529805312"}]},"mutability":"Immutable","type":"MEDIA"}},{"key":"9","value":{"data":{"entityKey":"5d30fd94-8c3c-4d13-abdb-bf863b7c7f23","mediaItems":[{"localMediaId":"10","mediaCategory":"DraftTweetImage","mediaId":"2070091077475049472"}]},"mutability":"Immutable","type":"MEDIA"}},{"key":"13","value":{"data":{"entityKey":"71bf7d5b-8523-